name: Industrial Machines
description:
This LoRA was created to produce images with a high tech industrial vibe. It was trained on a number of high resolution images of industrial equipment and tends towards an industrial colour palette (golds, silvers, teals). At high weights and in prompts without clear direction it will make photos of industrial equipment, but with direction it will make some pretty crazy robots :) . Trigger word is "mshn" and for humanoid subjects I've had the best success with "mshn robot".

Support me on Patreon to get access to all of my latest stuff, or check out my AI art pages: https://linktr.ee/mooncryptowow
